{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight along side your allies in this <strong>fantasy based arena </strong>PvP game, primarily focussed on archery combat. With more classes coming in the future. Created by Inspire Game Studios, a team of 2 brothers. Focusing primarily on fast paced arena gameplay, providing the game with a perfect place for balance and iteration before exploring additional mechanics and gamemodes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461600/extras/ProjectSparrow_Overview.png?t=1738109382\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461600/extras/Bio_Icon_23x21.png?t=1738109382\" /><strong>ENTER THE ARENA</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight alongside your allies in our 3v3 arena mode. Every round, players can change their loadout and choose between different arrow types, movement, ultimate and utility abilities. Stun your enemies with lightning, deny areas with fire arrows or cover up openings with smoke. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461600/extras/Bio_Icon_23x21.png?t=1738109382\" /><strong>TRAINING RANGE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Perfect your aim in the training range, providing different target types against AI and Bots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461600/extras/Bio_Icon_23x21.png?t=1738109382\" /><strong>DEDICATED SERVERS AND PLAYER COUNT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Please note queue times for matchmaking may be long, please use the Discord server if you are struggling to find a game. Dedicated server region availability is currently only supported in the following reg